Citation.sAbstract: Vapor-liquid equilibrium of binary mixtures of (benzene + 2,2,2-trifluoroethanol) and (toluene + 2,2,2-  trifluoroethanol) were measured in a dynamic recirculation still at pressure 102 kPa. The experimental results  were tested for thermodynamic consistency and were well-represented by the NRTL and UNIQUAC equations.  The two systems are azeotropic.
Citation.sTitle: Experimental Isobaric Vapor-Liquid Equilibria of Binary Mixtures of 2,2,2-Trifluoroethanol with Benzene or Toluene
